OL,3,CTeenager took own life after
OL,4,C'relentless bullying', inquest hears
OL,6,FA teenager who took her own life after
OL,7,Frelentless bullying had not been
OL,8,Fassessed by mental health officials
OL,9,Fdespite having self-harmed in class,
OL,10,Fan inquest has heard.
OL,12,FWillow-Tarriss Shannon Lynette Lee,
OL,13,Fknown as Ollie, died in Barnsley in
OL,14,FOctober 2024 after a struggle with her
OL,15,Fmental health. She was also waiting
OL,16,Ffor an assessment for autism at the
OL,17,Ftime of her death.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
