OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778097963
OL,3,CTeenager took own life after
OL,4,C'relentless bullying', inquest hears
OL,6,FAn inquest into the 14-year-old's
OL,7,Fdeath opened on Wednesday, after her
OL,8,Fmum said she was subjected to
OL,9,Frelentless bullying.
OL,11,FThe hearing at Sheffield Medico-Legal
OL,12,FCentre also heard Willow's school -
OL,13,FBarnsley Academy - failed to carry out
OL,14,Frisk assessments after she self-harmed
OL,15,Ftwice in class in the months before
OL,16,Fher death.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
