OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778097963
OL,3,CTeenager took own life after
OL,4,C'relentless bullying', inquest hears
OL,6,FMary Potter, the school's safeguarding
OL,7,Flead, gave evidence on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fwhere it emerged Ollie had suffered
OL,9,Fhomophobic abuse, had been dragged
OL,10,Fover grass, sprayed with deodorant and
OL,11,Feven told to harm or kill herself.
OL,13,FOllie had also used sharp objects in
OL,14,Fclass to hurt herself in the months
OL,15,Fbefore her death, it was heard, but no
OL,16,Fsafety assessments were drawn up.
OL,18,FShe made two suicide attempts while in
OL,19,FYear nine, returning in February 2024
OL,20,Fafter time off.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
