FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778097963
OL,3,CTeenager took own life after
OL,4,C'relentless bullying', inquest hears
OL,6,FThe school admitted in court it should
OL,7,Fhave drawn up safety support plans,
OL,8,Fbut said it believed the support
OL,9,Fprovided was "appropriate".
OL,11,FDescribing her daughter as "an
OL,12,Fextraordinary girl who brought chaos
OL,13,Fand light into every space she
OL,14,Fentered", Ollie's mum Courtney has
OL,15,Fsince called for bullying to be made a
OL,16,Fcriminal offence.
OL,26,@qD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
