PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778097963
OL,3,CTeenager took own life after
OL,4,C'relentless bullying', inquest hears
OL,6,FSpeaking on Wednesday, Ollie's father
OL,7,FJosh said: "I clearly remember talking
OL,8,Fto someone at the council and stating
OL,9,Fthat if anything else were to happen
OL,10,Fto Willow going forward I would
OL,11,Fpersonally hold the school and the
OL,12,Fcouncil accountable."
OL,14,FCourtney meanwhile said she supported
OL,15,Fher child "unconditionally" and had
OL,16,Falways accepted Ollie's gender
OL,17,Fidentity.
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@UO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
