PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1778097963
OL,3,CTeenager took own life after
OL,4,C'relentless bullying', inquest hears
OL,6,F"I saw a young person trying to
OL,7,Funderstand themselves in a world which
OL,8,Fdid not always make that easy," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FCourtney claimed she raised concerns
OL,12,Fabout Ollie's mental health
OL,13,Frepeatedly, and that she may never
OL,14,Fhave taken her life had she been
OL,15,Fassessed by a mental health team.
OL,17,FThe inquest, due to last until the end
OL,18,Fof the week, is also due to hear from
OL,19,Fmental health officials.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@_O]
